Description: .. image:: https://travis-ci.com/educrot/SPOCK_chilean.svg?token=JyPx6cqUzxMxHWAk8xyS&branch=master
            :target: https://travis-ci.com/educrot/SPOCK
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/docs-dev-green.svg
